Definition: an ethnic Kurdish group of Sunni extremists formed in the late 1980s in southeastern Turkey
Example: seeks to replace Turkey's secular regime with an Islamic state and strict shariah law; responsible for bombings and the torture and murder of Turkish and Kurdish journalists and businessmen; receives support from Iran
Synonyms: terrorist_organization, i, noun, act, terrorism, c, location, Turkey, r, an, ethnic, Kurdish, group, of, Sunni, extremists, formed, in, the, late, s, southeastern, seeks, to, replace, secular, regime, with, Islamic, state, and, strict, shariah, law, responsible, for, bombings, torture, murder, Turkish, journalists, businessmen, receives, support, from, Iran
Category: noun.group
